Author: ziyal79
Text: You shouldn't feel guilty. Honestly. You told a friend who cares about you that you're having a hard time. That's okay. It's okay to ask for help. \*It's okay to need help and it's okay to want help\*  It's also okay to be ambivalent about wanting help. It's actually pretty normal. Try to go easy on yourself, you haven't done anything wrong. You confided in a friend. That's okay. It's going to be okay.
